data.description: Large 4 bedroom/3 bath split foyer floorplan in convenient Lithia Springs location. Carpet in the bedrooms, newer tile in bathroom floors. Laminate flooring in the kitchen, dining room, family room and hallway. Kitchen cabinets have been painted, newer countertops, newer gas stove, microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator included. Spacious 4th bedroom downstairs with access to a 3rd bathroom. Nice master bedroom and bath with a large, tiled separate shower and garden tub. Huge fenced back yard with tons of room for the kids to play.
